Hi,

Thanks for writing to Dr. Math.

That symbol is "sigma", the Greek letter for "s". It stands for
"summation". You can find more information about it at:

  http://www.ucl.ac.uk/Mathematics/geomath/level2/series/ser4.html

Does this help?  Please feel free to write back with any questions you
may have.

